Class AuthSubcommandBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • ru.baronessdev.paid.auth.api.subcommands.AuthSubcommandBuilder
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BaronessAuthAPIComponent

    public class AuthSubcommandBuilder
extends java.lang.Object
implements BaronessAuthAPIComponent
    Builder для создания субкоманд.

    Пример использования: 

     
 new AuthSubcommandBuilder("smack", new YourSubcommand()
     .setDescription("[player] - smack player's butt")
     .setAutoRemove(true)
     .setShow(false) // секретная команда
     .build();
    See Also:
    AuthIconsAPI, AuthSubcommandExecutor
